data.description: A charming two story residence in established Monarch subdivision, less than 10 minutes from treasure valley marketplace and freeway access. This updated open concept floor plan gives you a large family room with gas fireplace, raised bar and ample indoor and outdoor gathering space with a covered patio, new landscape and above ground pool perfect for entertaining and everyday living. Stunning LVP wood floors cover the main level and continue upstairs where new plush carpet lines the bedrooms. Kitchen features two toned cabinets with black hardware, pantry and new black stainless appliances. The upper level is dedicated to sleeping quarters and includes four bedrooms and two baths. The primary suite features large walk in closet, dual vanities, soaker tub with separate shower and vaulted ceilings. Garage is converted into a den which can be used as a work shop, office or many other endless possibilities! Home is equipped with solar panels and has an assumable FHA loan with low interest rate!
